OL,3,CMan, 49, dies after skydive in Devon,
OL,4,Cpolice say
OL,6,FA man has died following a skydive in
OL,7,FDevon.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to
OL,10,FDunkeswell Aerodrome, Honiton, at
OL,11,Faround 1pm on Saturday due to concerns
OL,12,Ffor the welfare of a skydiver.
OL,14,FA 49-year-old man was pronounced dead
OL,15,Fat the scene and his family have been
OL,16,Finformed.
OL,18,FA spokesman for Devon and Cornwall
OL,19,FPolice said scene guards remain in
OL,20,Fplace and inquiries are ongoing into
OL,21,Fthe incident.
