OL,3,CMan, 49, dies after skydive in Devon,
OL,4,Cpolice say
OL,6,FThe spokesman said: "Police were
OL,7,Fcalled to Dunkeswell Aerodrome just
OL,8,Fbefore 1pm today, Saturday 28
OL,9,FFebruary, following concerns for the
OL,10,Fwelfare of a male skydiver.
OL,12,F"Emergency services attended the
OL,13,Fscene, where sadly a 49-year-old man
OL,14,Fwas confirmed deceased.
OL,16,F"His family have been informed."
OL,18,FThis incident comes less than a year
OL,19,Fafter two people died while taking
OL,20,Fpart in a tandem jump at the same
OL,21,Fairfield.
