OL,3,CMan, 49, dies after skydive in Devon,
OL,4,Cpolice say
OL,6,FMother-of-four Belinda Taylor, 48,
OL,7,Ffrom Totnes, Devon, and Adam Harrison,
OL,8,F30, from Bournemouth, Dorset, died
OL,9,Fwhile skydiving in June last year.
OL,11,FThe site is located in the Blackdown
OL,12,FHills and advertises activities
OL,13,Fincluding skydiving, wing walking and
OL,14,Fhelicopter training.
